对方小时闪避掉对方的攻击，以柔克刚！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好好利用好你的闪避牌，不管敌人伤害多高都不怕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏含有上百种不同的卡牌与宝物，之后也会更新的~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有，各种可爱的魔物娘！就凭这个也该来玩玩了吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265880/extras/27c1e7301913946abc8ca2f9f3b1b5a7.avif?t=1733277722\" width=485 height=600 /></span></p>",
